My Habit Tracker for assignment #1

Testing code:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YqUH8_xFxLM&feature=youtu.be


Main Activities showcases Today's Habits, with a menu option to add new Habits. Those habits can be completed or deleted.
A button can be pressed to goto a completed Activity, where all the habits are shown. Those can be deleted or a button can
be pressed which shows all the habit completions.

Coding was based of lonelyTwitter then tweaked to meet demands. Some code was sample off the internet which will be shown 
by a commented hyperlink.

